  Strength: 8
  EntityName: Patch Manager
  Description: '<color=#FF4444>50 HP</color> | <color=#FFAA00>8 ATK</color> | <color=#00CCFF>40
    EN</color>

    Automatically monitors, downloads, and installs software updates,
    thereby eliminating critical vulnerabilities and bugs in operating systems and
    applications. It centrally manages the patch deployment process, allowing IT
    specialists to test updates before rolling them out to the entire environment
    to maintain infrastructure stability.

    Stuns enemies.

    <color=#BF00FF>Enemies:
    Worm, Zero Day Exploit.</color>'
